Comment: 10,0:07:49.35,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Comment: 10,0:07:51.11,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want to do is use magic to make people happy.
Comment: 10,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can do...
Comment: 10,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand a thing.
