Comment: 10,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Diana.
Comment: 10,0:09:43.60,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an urgent message regarding Akko.
Comment: 10,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Comment: 10,0:09:51.31,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko has yet to return from her trip into town.
Comment: 10,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about that?
Comment: 10,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not meet Akko in the city?
Comment: 10,0:10:05.58,0:10:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 10,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Comment: 10,0:10:11.42,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, may we continue our conversation from this afternoon?
Comment: 10,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little tied up with other things right now.
Comment: 10,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll get right to the point.
Comment: 10,0:10:23.29,0:10:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no records of a student by the name of Ursula Callistis attending this school.
Comment: 10,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name is Chariot du Nord.
Comment: 10,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Shiny Chariot, correct?
Comment: 10,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Comment: 10,0:10:43.20,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You ran into Akko earlier, didn't you?
Comment: 10,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me what happened!
Comment: 10,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Comment: 10,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who saw your show became unable to use magic?
Comment: 10,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt Akko.
Comment: 10,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't chase after her?
Comment: 10,0:11:07.17,0:11:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you left her alone in that condition and returned by yourself?
Comment: 10,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ursula!
Comment: 10,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 10,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer be of help to Akko.
Comment: 10,0:11:18.62,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! Now is the time she most needs you by her side!
Comment: 10,0:11:24.47,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but there's something else I must be doing.
Comment: 10,0:11:29.14,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can anything possibly be more important\Nthan worrying about Akko right now?!
Comment: 10,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. That's enough.
Comment: 10,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find Akko.
Comment: 10,0:11:44.23,0:11:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more disappointed in what you did today\Nthan all that you've done in the past.
Comment: 10,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... take care of Akko.
Comment: 10,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko still hasn't come back?
Comment: 10,0:12:07.94,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she may still be somewhere out in town.
Comment: 10,0:12:11.93,0:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you learn anything new?
Comment: 10,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Comment: 10,0:12:18.40,0:12:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. It's really Chariot's fault that Akko can't fly?
Comment: 10,0:12:23.20,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no chance Akko could've imagined that.
Comment: 10,0:12:26.47,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think she's not planning to come back...
Comment: 10,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Comment: 10,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko would never leave over something like that...
Comment: 10,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Comment: 10,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean it.
Comment: 10,0:12:39.71,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But how does Professor Ursula know all that?
Comment: 10,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you in due time.
Comment: 10,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing now is to find Akko.
Comment: 10,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going too!
Comment: 10,0:12:49.89,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Comment: 10,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then we'll start looking around the terminal.
Comment: 10,0:12:53.95,0:12:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. I will start my search from the Leyline.
Comment: 10,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Let's go!
Comment: 10,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:13:21.54,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, if Akko doesn't come back,\Nshe'd better hope I don't find her. {implying she'd knock her silly or something. the internal contradiction is intentional}{## i like it}
Comment: 10,0:13:30.92,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Akko's a genius at making people run themselves ragged.
Comment: 10,0:13:36.22,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucy!
Comment: 10,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find her at the terminal.
Comment: 10,0:13:42.64,0:13:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not on this side either.\NMaybe she's not in the area.
Comment: 10,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We should check out the plaza, just in case.{my memory says they used this word at some point in the past, but it would be nigh impossible to find}{## maybe in a sign}
Comment: 10,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Comment: 10,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this.
Comment: 10,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Akko to go away!
Comment: 10,0:14:02.53,0:14:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even considered the thought that Akko might leave.
Comment: 10,0:14:08.77,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? If Akko never comes back...
Comment: 10,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Comment: 10,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko's an idiot.
Comment: 10,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd never think about anything that difficult.
Comment: 10,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 10,0:14:25.08,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She'll come back moaning\Nthat she's hungry, like she always does.
Comment: 10,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko!
Comment: 10,0:14:57.21,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you warmed up somewhat?
Comment: 10,0:15:01.76,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been freezing. I was shocked\Nto see you sitting out there in the cold.{## why do they always wear skirts anyway, even in fucking winter. not even tights or anything}{blame japan—I mean britain}
Comment: 10,0:15:12.31,0:15:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked Professor Ursula about what happened with you and Chariot.
Comment: 10,0:15:24.49,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there was something I wanted to show you.
Comment: 10,0:15:33.67,0:15:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chariot premium card... {if I was following Aikatsu rules it would've been capitalized}{## maybe "Chariot's Premium Card"}
Comment: 10,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you were collecting them as well.
Comment: 10,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have this?
Comment: 10,0:15:42.95,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I used to look up to Shiny Chariot as a child too.
Comment: 10,0:15:47.64,0:15:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You looked up to her?
Comment: 10,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was infatuated.
Comment: 10,0:15:54.13,0:15:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, those from the world of magic\Nwere already looking down on her.
Comment: 10,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't collect these cards but in secret.
Comment: 10,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure from those around me made me give up on seeing a show myself.
Comment: 10,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless nights, I could only dream of seeing Chariot's show.
Comment: 10,0:16:12.82,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, my mother arranged for me to see one overseas, where nobody would notice.
Comment: 10,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You went that far to see her?
Comment: 10,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, to your country.
Comment: 10,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you were at that show too?
Comment: 10,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fantastic.
Comment: 10,0:16:31.97,0:16:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember that night as clearly as if it were yesterday.
Comment: 10,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}There was a time when Diana became\Ncompletely unable to use magic.{## not gonna check, i assume you looked it up}
Comment: 10,0:16:40.61,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that when you became unable to use magic...
Comment: 10,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew about that?
Comment: 10,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Andrew told me.
Comment: 10,0:16:49.63,0:16:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He also said you never gave up and worked hard until you got your magic back.
Comment: 10,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 10,0:16:59.72,0:17:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to us was an unfortunate accident.
Comment: 10,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will not give you my sympathy.
Comment: 10,0:17:06.96,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the greatest proof that it is possible to regain that lost power.
Comment: 10,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are, Diana.
Comment: 10,0:17:18.59,0:17:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though your ability was sucked up too, \Nyou worked hard and became an amazing witch.
Comment: 10,0:17:25.44,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But here I am, still unable to even fly.
Comment: 10,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you know why I didn't give up?
Comment: 10,0:17:38.38,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you had to become the Cavendish family head?
Comment: 10,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is one part of it, of course.
Comment: 10,0:17:43.48,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a young girl, that reason alone could not have compelled me to keep going.
Comment: 10,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the same as you.
Comment: 10,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:17:55.06,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, was charmed by Shiny Chariot's magic.
Comment: 10,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I saw Chariot's magic.
Comment: 10,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart was racing with pure happiness.
Comment: 10,0:18:12.74,0:18:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the preciousness of magic deep inside me.
Comment: 10,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chariot filled me with emotion.
Comment: 10,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That in itself was my greatest support back then.
Comment: 10,0:18:39.22,0:18:45.84,Default,,15,15,0,,Unfortunately, the more I learned of magic and the more aware I became of the expectations placed on me, {I see how you misunderstood my structure}
Comment: 10,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the further my heart grew away from Chariot. {because it's cause and effect}
Comment: 10,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't continue with these childish dreams."
Comment: 10,0:18:59.92,0:19:04.16,Default,,15,15,0,,Telling myself I had to become an adult, I closed the lid. {metaphorically}
Comment: 10,0:19:05.68,0:19:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, the true reason I entered Luna Nova
Comment: 10,0:19:09.01,0:19:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,was because it was the school Chariot went to.
Comment: 10,0:19:14.35,0:19:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first met, I couldn't stand you at all.
Comment: 10,0:19:18.73,0:19:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:19:19.98,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You went around telling everyone you loved Chariot,\Nand your grades and magic couldn't have been worse.
Comment: 10,0:19:25.08,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You always acted without thinking\Nand caused trouble for everyone.
Comment: 10,0:19:29.76,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, \Nyou were able to do things I couldn't.
Comment: 10,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic had a mysterious charm to it.
Comment: 10,0:19:38.55,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was envious of you.
Comment: 10,0:19:42.00,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were?
Comment: 10,0:19:45.04,0:19:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking back, the reason I tried to leave Luna Nova\Nmight have been to run away from you.{## maybe "one reason"?}{nix like a bix}
Comment: 10,0:19:52.46,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to avoid facing the reality of you being far closer to Chariot than I was.
Comment: 10,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Diana...
Comment: 10,0:20:01.31,0:20:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give this to you.
Comment: 10,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it with the meaning of the card.
Comment: 10,0:20:07.18,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"A believing heart is your magic." {I translate for this feeling of ecstatic vindication}{## i edit for the existential dread of starting the monday on 4 hours of sleep max; but yeah, super cool this worked out}
Comment: 10,0:20:11.03,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe as well.
Comment: 10,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in your believing heart.
Comment: 10,0:20:15.89,0:20:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic is stronger than anyone else's.
Comment: 10,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Akko!
Comment: 10,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai—Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't go anywhere, right?
Comment: 10,0:20:34.35,0:20:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't quit school, right?
Comment: 10,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Comment: 10,0:20:40.30,0:20:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'll never quit, not until\NI become a splendid witch!{## had typo}
Comment: 10,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? {falling in love all over again}
Comment: 10,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! I'm sorry I made you worry.{## that "promise" came outta nowhere}
Comment: 10,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Comment: 10,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You here, Akko?!
Comment: 10,0:21:05.04,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amanda! Constanze and Jasminka too.
Comment: 10,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko says she isn't going anywhere!
Comment: 10,0:21:10.42,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's exactly what I told you.
Comment: 10,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, you kids must be freezing. {I didn't want to say anything but this episode suffers from a large amount of reused words in multiple parts}
Comment: 10,0:21:16.09,0:21:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink up! It's on the house.
Comment: 10,0:21:19.06,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 10,0:21:21.10,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akko, don't tell me you were crying.
Comment: 10,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't crying! The cold just made my eyes—
Comment: 10,0:21:27.15,0:21:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're full of it. I can still see the tears.
Comment: 10,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Comment: 10,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you certainly were crying.
Comment: 10,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Comment: 10,0:21:53.59,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about how I wanted you to see this.
Comment: 10,0:21:57.63,0:21:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Comment: 10,0:21:59.05,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir Fuel Spirit.
Comment: 10,0:22:02.77,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I harvested it from all around the country.
Comment: 10,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't have done this without you.
Comment: 10,0:22:07.92,0:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your Dream Fuel Spirit experiments\Nthat helped me complete this.
Comment: 10,0:22:13.73,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you deserve some gratitude.
Comment: 10,0:22:16.63,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. My plan has entered its final stage.
Comment: 10,0:22:23.06,0:22:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Comment: 10,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will stop you.
